MAZESIZE EQU 1840

; MAP Elements
WALL     EQU 0
ENDPOS   EQU 1
HALL     EQU 2
DECPOS   EQU 3
VISPOS   EQU 4
FINPOS   EQU 5

; Direction Definitions
NORTH    EQU 0
